whisper Test scoping and variable isolation

whisper Test 1: Loop variable should not exist after loop
for_each_house x claims 1 then 3 {
  raven x!
}
whisper After loop, x should not be accessible if we try to use it in another block

whisper Test 2: Variable shadowing in council branches
coin y claims 100!
council y greater_than 50 {
  y claims 999!
  raven y!
}
otherwise {
  raven y!
}
raven y!

whisper Test 3: Nested block with variable shadowing
coin z claims 10!
council z less_than 20 {
  z claims 50!
  raven z!
}
otherwise {
  raven 0!
}
raven z!

whisper Test 4: Loop with variable shadowing
coin i claims 1000!
for_each_house i claims 5 then 8 {
  raven i!
}
raven i!

whisper Test 5: While loop maintains independence
coin w claims 0!
while_winter w less_than 3 {
  w claims w unite 1!
  raven w!
}
raven w!
